“You have more to do than be weighed down by pretty or beautiful. You are a fiery heart and a wicked brain. Do not let your soul be defined by it’s shell”

summary: SLEEPOVER PARTY~! Happy late birthday Stella Star ( @a-s-ced / @stelloink ) !!! Featuring @paradoxii / @ddkinzart + our ocs as...
caption:
SLEEPOVER PARTY~!

Happy late birthday Stella Star ( @a-s-ced / @stelloink ) !!! Featuring @paradoxii / @ddkinzart + our ocs as dolls. 

I am very sorry this is late, school kept me a bit busy + this ended up taking longer than I thought it would lol. 

But I wanted to draw a piece of us hanging out because 1) I thought it would be fun. And 2) it’s a better way to express how important of a friend you are to me. It’s getting close to the five-year mark of when we first met and starting becoming friends. Since then you have never stopped being supportive of me not only when it came to Camilla but when real life issues popped up as well. 

Five years you stayed by my side, longer than a lot of people in my real life have. I know we don’t get to hang out in real life and I know time differences sometimes makes it hard to actually have conversations, but to me, you are more of a real friend than most others I know. Your friendship is very dear to me, as are you. You hold a really special place in my heart. I am so glad you were born and that we got the chance to meet. I hope you had a great birthday and that you’ll have nothing but good vibes for the rest of the year. 

I love you so much! Thank you for everything~  ♡ ♡ ♡
